'''Dawlatzai''' ({{lang-ps|'''دولتزئ'''}}) are several [[Pashtun people|Pashtun]] tribes in eastern [[Afghanistan]] and western [[Pakistan]]. Dawlatzis live in Logar, Samangan, Paktia, Paktika, Khost, Baghlan, Nangarhar, Balkh Tajurghan, and Faryab provinces of Afghanistan. 

